          </LEXSubDomains>
          <LEXSenses>
            <LEXSense LanguageCode="en" LastEdited="2021-07-08 22:11:19" LastEditedBy="">
              <DefinitionLong/>
              <DefinitionShort>to move quickly and energetically toward some objective</DefinitionShort>
              <Glosses>
                <Gloss>to hasten</Gloss>
                <Gloss>to run</Gloss>
                <Gloss>to press forward</Gloss>
                <Gloss>to press on</Gloss>
              </Glosses>
              <Comments>In {S:05000301400006} διώκω is to be understood in a literal sense, though the entire context is figurative. For interpreting the expression {L:κατὰ σκοπὸν διώκω&lt;SDBG:διώκω:000006&gt;} as an idiom, see {D:89.56}.</Comments>
            </LEXSense>
