          </LEXSubDomains>
          <LEXSenses>
            <LEXSense LanguageCode="en" LastEdited="2021-07-08 22:11:19" LastEditedBy="">
              <DefinitionLong/>
              <DefinitionShort>to systematically organize a program to oppress and harass people{N:001}</DefinitionShort>
              <Glosses>
                <Gloss>to persecute</Gloss>
                <Gloss>to harass</Gloss>
                <Gloss>persecution</Gloss>
              </Glosses>
              <Comments>In a number of languages the equivalent of ‘to persecute’ is simply ‘to cause to suffer,’ but persecution is also expressed in terms of ‘to be mean to’ or ‘to threaten’ or ‘to chase from place to place.’</Comments>
            </LEXSense>
